          a(href='https://github.com/guidotorresmx') @guidotorresmx
          | . Source code can be found at 
          a(href='https://github.com/guidotorresmx/blog') @guidotorresmx/resume
          |  This blog uses Pug, Sass, Hexo, Bootstrap and Bulma.

      div
        span!= theme.user && theme.user.footnotes

    script(async defer src="https://buttons.github.io/buttons.js")
    block script